OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Fthrough the evening with a few
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain, mostly over the
OL,8,FPennines. Clear spells then developing
OL,9,Fthrough the early hours along with
OL,10,Feasing winds. Feeling mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FDry and warm on Friday with
OL,13,Fhazy sunshine throughout the day and
OL,14,Flight winds. Cloudy and mild overnight
OL,15,Fwith a risk of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
